content: madjin: Focused on improving the project's deployment process and enabling multi-repository support. They delivered a key fix to dynamically handle stats for multiple repositories (elizaos/elizaos.github.io#157) and authored a new deployment guide to help others fork the project (elizaos/elizaos.github.io#158), proactively identifying and closing five related issues. This work involved changes primarily to documentation and configuration files.
